{"tid":94830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那指示共諜：製造反對派系間的對立 瓦解反抗","createTime":"2017-01-25T13:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T01:51:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"346603e18260af034bc508d6237c596a15b98b99","tid":94830,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/102438_154fc0ec6742211c55c2f92ff3444e39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F102438_154fc0ec6742211c55c2f92ff3444e39.jpg&h=0b90f821&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 維護大局穩定， 預防群眾反抗，利用群眾貪生怕死等的心理，進行精神維穩。宣揚民主改良，培養民眾成為溫和民主派，決不反對黨和政府，把責任推給貪官污吏，規避政權風險。 <br />\n<br />\n2. 引導認知差異：製造矛盾而引起鬥爭，產生派系分別，瓦解民主抵抗派團結 <br />\n<br />\n3. 引導群眾認知：主要責任是體制問題，避免群眾發現政府操縱體制。利用老年人思維彊化，轉移政府責任去體制和法律的不健全，要堅信支那會自我改良！ <br />\n<br />\n4. 宣傳覺醒理論：給予頑固民主派群眾一個逃避現實的精神麻醉，安慰民心。讓群眾多宣揚民主要依靠全民覺醒，不能採取鬥爭！重點是引導全民輿論走向溫和，放棄攻擊。保護政府安全 <br />\n<br />\n5. 實施釣魚執法圍捕危險分子，消滅潛在危害 <br />\n<br />\n6. 團聚老年人，培養順民耍嘴皮子愛好者，發佈各種虛假腐敗內幕信息，引導群眾談論腐敗官員，消除民主思維。 <br />\n<br />\n*課程培訓要求：堅持網絡維穩，搞好輿論引導，破壞敵對勢力，瓦解群眾敵對政府的意識，防止各地暴力對抗"},{"pid":"b8f39118fbae4bb40c7fff471f203bbd45d15f19","tid":94830,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:35:57.000Z","msg":"販民同埋支持永續基本法個班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8292b52bcf70bf688721abc06f5ec5cc335705f","tid":94830,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:41:45.000Z","msg":"阿狗都知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628f619482a8429405b704b0d0d7d79669099728","tid":94830,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:45:05.000Z","msg":"😣"},{"pid":"85d9612e95a511afba5fb5fb875559a2181513f1","tid":94830,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>販民同埋支持永續基本法個班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有青狗班垃圾"},{"pid":"42f9fec971807e9f0a77766490c5f4b6763e20f8","tid":94830,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:29:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿狗都知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n5毛狗知但香港豬多嗎"},{"pid":"6c0246b2a3f965b91d84279c7dd68f3a42b3d490","tid":94830,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:51:49.000Z","msg":"［支那的事］ 網絡維穩重點：防止各地武力對抗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/94071?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/94071?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n連登去高登再黎返連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}